    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_14",
    "text": "that the different Puma match ball in the competition played a part because it is different to what they are used to in the Premier League.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.20702402621498925,
      0.5493551587370772,
      0.37338262878712786,
      0.5873015871564595
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_15",
    "text": "The Gunners boss said: \"We kicked a lot of balls over the bar, and it's tricky that these balls fly a lot so there's details that we can do better.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.20702402932707958,
      0.5872093024662645,
      0.3807763333357638,
      0.6366279067488517
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_16",
    "text": "\"It's very different to a Premier League ball, and you have to adapt to that because it flies different, when you touch it the grip is very different as well so you adapt to that.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.20702402913243956,
      0.6366279072991132,
      0.3715341923138197,
      0.6947674416228827
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_20",
    "text": "forward in Europe at the moment.\" Newcastle boss Eddie Howe hailed his team's performance and also that of danger man Isak.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.39001848874594613,
      0.6468023258845952,
      0.5545286470483015,
      0.6860465112934256
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_9",
    "text": "MAN OF THE MATCH",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.03873757523385479,
      0.6697134559842501,
      0.15904430866309865,
      0.6878446837046016
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 21
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_21",
    "text": "Howe said: \"Alex played very well in the first half today, he looked really good physically, his pace and movements were giving them a problem. I was delighted with how he performed.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3900184838137139,
      0.686011904739402,
      0.55822550530408,
      0.7442956349689739
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 22
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_41",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
      0.03620161738509071,
      0.6881984058090829,
      0.16140615635251934,
      0.8867746396880511
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 23
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_17",
    "text": "\"It's just half-time. When I see the team play, and how we deal with a lot of situations and play against a very good team I must say I have full belief that we can go out there and do it.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.20702402621498925,
      0.6961805553706465,
      0.3789279137845841,
      0.7529761903200615
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 24
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_23",
    "text": "JFC",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.7097966729904739,
      0.7005813954231126,
      0.7319778186915965,
      0.7107558136757245
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 25
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_22",
    "text": "\"When Alex is in that mood, as he was in the first half, he is a brilliant player for us. It goes without saying that he does the hard work and raises our overall level.\"",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3900184853647119,
      0.745535714431063,
      0.5619223650433328,
      0.793650793842649
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 26
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_18",
    "text": "Isak scored his 10th goal in nine games (celebrating, above) and his strike partner Gordon claimed: \"I don't think there's a better centre",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.20702403017778345,
      0.7543604653538614,
      0.3715341948603069,
      0.7921626984655926
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 27
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_45",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
      0.4798593294358457,
      0.804709804205247,
      0.5218194796398329,
      0.8347322978670635
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 28
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_43",
    "text": "",
    "canon_role": "picture",
    "bbox": [
      0.17730614314329576,
      0.8088857714671517,
      0.3806050207755019,
      0.9758386036706349
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 29
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_27",
    "text": "difference a top striker makes. Alexander Isak took his chance while Arsenal's forward line wasted every opening. It is now 50 goals for Isak in all competitions since he joined Newcastle for £63million in August 2022.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5304990786423075,
      0.8110119046303904,
      0.6746765269029789,
      0.8896329364242609
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 30
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_24",
    "text": "BY JOHN CROSS Chief Football Writer X @johncrossmirror",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.38632162875780957,
      0.811011904850415,
      0.47319778139369817,
      0.8358134919688152
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 31
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_25",
    "text": "THE Toon Army are already singing about Wembley.",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.3858093566982851,
      0.837209302447095,
      0.5268022174219293,
      0.8677035936165199
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 32
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_34",
    "text": "The squad looks wafer-thin and they lack a proven goalscorer. As good as Kai Havertz was last season, the Arsenal striker horribly mistimed a second-half header (far right) and a chance to haul his team back into the tie.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.8280961189921187,
      0.8501984128823001,
      0.9685767099428073,
      0.9273313490049937
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 33
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_10",
    "text": "ALEXANDER ISAK Scored one, had a hand in the other",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.04805914735257759,
      0.854651162590852,
      0.14787430902450188,
      0.8808139532743485
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 34
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_26",
    "text": "And no wonder. Newcastle have got one foot in the Carabao Cup final on March 16 after a hugely impressive display at the Emirates.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.38447319980304184,
      0.8677325583771173,
      0.5268022204442684,
      0.9171626982717944
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 35
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_32",
    "text": "Even more worryingly, they have hit the wall at just the wrong time.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6801993991705652,
      0.8705357143220515,
      0.8225508324212341,
      0.8997929917314704
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 36
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_36",
    "text": "He is the reason why they are dreaming of their first major trophy in 56 years.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5323475040825651,
      0.8895348840665235,
      0.6728280970038054,
      0.9186507934352137
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 37
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_11",
    "text": "NEXT THREE...",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.03509527271668742,
      0.8938147783391285,
      0.11093060718164208,
      0.9085108025791379
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 38
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_31",
    "text": "They face Manchester United in the FA Cup third round on Sunday and are already six points behind Liverpool in the title race, having played a game more.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6802218127382679,
      0.8997093025147141,
      0.822550834122642,
      0.9578488369787769
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 39
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_12",
    "text": "ARSENAL",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.038817006810496976,
      0.9069767442244403,
      0.06839186614082769,
      0.9142441857658699
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 40
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_39",
    "text": "Sun | Man United (home) .....FAC | Wed | Tottenham (home) .... | Jan 18 | Aston Villa (home). | NEWCASTLE Sun | Bromley (home). . FAC | Wed | Wolves (home) ...PL | Jan 18 | Bournemouth (home) ...PL",
    "canon_role": "table",
    "bbox": [
      0.03751020059290356,
      0.9138657235174162,
      0.15679778299721006,
      0.9700019634589947
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 41
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_30",
    "text": "Isak even played a part in Newcastle's second goal as it was his cross shot which led to Anthony Gordon (left) firing in the rebound to give them a huge advantage for the second leg. Arsenal need a minor miracle to turn the semi-final on its head in next month's return, but they look ragged, tired and as if they are running on empty.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5323475053137453,
      0.917151162711356,
      0.6746765255820474,
      0.9781976741699107
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 42
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_28",
    "text": "Eddie Howes men looked sharp, slick and dangerous while Arsenal were horribly flat with their season now in serious danger of fading away.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3844731984745587,
      0.9186046514434323,
      0.5268022187428609,
      0.9665697673385152
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 43
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_35",
    "text": "That miss summed up Arsenal's shortcomings. They were wasteful in attack sloppy in defence and lacking ideas in midfield. They racked",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.8280961230894693,
      0.9287790699953344,
      0.9685767099428073,
      0.978197674151742
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 44
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_33",
    "text": "Arsenal are still in the Champions League, but they look short of ideas, attacking threat and quality with Bukayo Saka out injured for the next two months.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.6820702411927126,
      0.9578373015828571,
      0.822550834122642,
      0.9781976741699107
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058",
    "order": 45
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_Daily Mirror 2025-1-8@magazinesclubnew_page_058_29",
    "text": "In truth, it was all about the",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3955637728397733,
      0.9665178572374235,
      0.5268022204442684,
